name: Two Maharajas
description:
Two kings (maharajas) fight over a small village. 
Depicts the imbalance between the rich and powerful and the labour class. 
The powerful leans over the life of the poor and often fights in the name of their protection. However, it is usually just a show of dominance and power and a battle of egos. People are usually like to live a peaceful life and no matter what would avoid any type of violent solution to their problems
